<div class="row-full color-scheme-navy d-flex align-items-center fh">
    <div class="row-lg  d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="row-half d-flex flex-column">
            <h3 class="text-white-50 animate py-sm-3">Founded on the principle of</h3>
            <h1 class="text-white animate">empowering women to take back control of their health.</h1>
            <div class="row-full py-5 animate">
                <a class="cta-button-w my-5 p-3" asp-controller="Contact" asp-action="Index">Take Back Your Health</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row-full color-scheme-none">
    <div class="row-lg">
        <div class="row-half d-flex flex-column nomauto">
            <h3>Our services</h3>
            <p class="animate">
                Together, we incorporate an integrative approach to make food enjoyable again, reduce your symptoms and truly feel well. By utilizing real, science-backed nutrition with functional lab testing, we take a deep dive into your health to address underlying causes to make sustainable changes to meet you where you are.
            </p>
        </div>
