    </div>
</div>

<div class="row-full color-scheme-none d-flex flex-column align-items-start">
    <div class="row-lg d-flex flex-wrap m-auto align-items-center" style="position: relative;">
        <partial name="_OrgansPartial" />
    </div>
</div>



<div class="row-full color-scheme-tan d-flex align-items-center">
    <div class="row-lg d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="row-half d-flex flex-column">
            <h3 class="animate">Schedule your free call</h3>
            <p class="animate">Knowing where to start can be difficult, book a free call to schedule a 1-1 meeting to beging your personal journey to health.</p>
            <div class="row-full py-5 animate">
                <a class="cta-button-w my-5 p-3" asp-controller="Contact" asp-action="Bookings">Book a Free Call</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row-full color-scheme-navy d-flex align-items-center fh">
    <div class="row-lg d-flex align-items-center">
        <div class="row-half d-flex flex-column">
            <h3 class="text-white-50 animate">Your feminine physiology is uniquely designed. </h3>
            <h1 class="animate">Your nutrition should be that way too.</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row-full color-scheme-none d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center hh">
    <div class="row-lg d-flex flex-wrap-reverse align-items-center">
        <div class="row-half m-auto d-flex flex-column">
            <h2 class="animate">Hey, I'm Amber</h2>
            <p class="animate">I’m a mama, wife, Registered Nurse and Candidate for a Board-Certified Nutrition Specialist. Through my own health struggles, I have discovered the awe-inspiring power of food and the impact true nourishment can have on your symptoms and diagnosis. Now, I have set out on a mission to empower other women to do the same, be informed of their health and truly feel well. The rumors are false: you can have your health and eat your cookies too.</p>
            <div class="row-full py-5 animate">
                <a class="cta-button-w my-5 p-3" asp-controller="Contact" asp-action="Index">Contact Me</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="m-auto row-half text-center">
            <img src="https://i.imgur.com/vzMPPtE.jpg" width="auto"  height="600px" alt="Amber Adkins, Owner and Founder of She Wellness Co." />
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

